                <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-8">
                    <h2>Fatbardh Veseli</h2>
                    <h3></h3>
                    <p>Fatbardh is a researcher at Goethe University Frankfurt in the area of security and privacy technologies. He has been involved in various European research and innovation projects in this field of privacy-enhancing identity management, and held talks at conferences and workshops word-wide. His main research interests, which is also core of his doctoral studies, include assessment and evaluation of Privacy-enhancing attribute-based credential technologies, identification of their challenges, and their applications in real life.</p>
